Guvf vf Gnfx 17 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Nabgure cngpu znqr naq frag va.  Frr, gung jnfa'g fb uneq.  Xrrc fraqvat
va xreary cngpurf bhgfvqr bs guvf punyyratr, gubfr ynml xreary
qrirybcref arrq nyy gur uryc gurl pna trg va pyrnavat hc gurve pbqr.

Vg vf gvzr gb fgneg chggvat gur qvssrerag cvrprf bs jung jr unir qbar va
gur cnfg gbtrgure, vagb n zhpu ynetre zbqhyr, qbvat zber pbzcyrk guvatf.
Zhpu zber yvxr jung n "erny" xreary zbqhyr unf gb qb.

Tb qvt hc lbhe pbqr sebz gnfx 06, gur zvfp pune qrivpr qevire, naq znxr
gur sbyybjvat punatrf:

 - Qryrgr gur ernq shapgvba.  Lbh qba'g arrq gung nalzber, fb znxr vg n
   jevgr-bayl zvfp qrivpr naq or fher gb frg gur zbqr bs gur qrivpr gb
   or jevgr-bayl, ol nalbar.  Vs lbh qb guvf evtug, hqri jvyy frg hc gur
   abqr nhgbzngvpnyyl jvgu gur pbeerpg crezvffvbaf.
 - Perngr n jnvg dhrhr, anzr vg "jrr_jnvg".
 - Va lbhe zbqhyr vavg shapgvba, perngr n xreary guernq, anzrq bs pbhefr
   "rhqlcghyn".
 - Gur guernq'f znva shapgvba fubhyq abg qb nalguvat ng guvf cbvag va
   gvzr, rkprcg znxr fher gb fuhgqbja vs nfxrq gb, naq jnvg ba gur
   "jrr_jnvg" jnvgdhrhr.
 - Va lbhe zbqhyr rkvg shapgvba, fuhg qbja gur xreary guernq lbh fgnegrq
   hc.

Ybnq naq haybnq gur zbqhyr naq "cebir" gung vg jbexf cebcreyl (gung gur
guernq vf perngrq, vg pna or sbhaq va gur cebprff yvfg, naq gung gur
qrivpr abqr vf perngrq jvgu gur pbeerpg crezvffvba inyhr.)  Fraq va gur
cebbs naq gur .p svyr sbe gur zbqhyr.

Or fher gb xrrc guvf pbqr nebhaq, nf jr jvyy or qbvat zber jvgu vg arkg
gvzr.
